* `M ‚âÉ·∂†À°[p, k] M‚ÇÇ`: `linear_equiv (witt_vector.fraction_ring.frobenius_ring_hom p k) M M‚ÇÇ`
* `Œ¶(p, k)`: `witt_vector.isocrystal.frobenius p k`
